  <h3 class="mt2">3 · The CNOT Gate &amp; Creating Entanglement</h3>
  <p>H gate on q₀ → CNOT(q₀→q₁): when control is in superposition, output is the Bell state (|00⟩+|11⟩)/√2. This proves entanglement — measuring one qubit determines the other.</p>
